In production environments, itâ€™s critical to ensure that all essential services like web servers remain available and healthy. During routine monitoring at xFusionCorp Industries, one of the monitoring tools reported that the Apache HTTP service was down on one of the application servers in Stratos DC.

Our goal was to:

Identify the faulty application host.

Fix the Apache service issue.

Ensure Apache is running on port 6300 on all app servers.

