This confirmed the service was up and reachable.

Final Result
âœ… Identified the cause of Apache failure (port conflict with sendmail).

âœ… Freed port 6300 by stopping the conflicting service.

âœ… Restarted Apache successfully.

âœ… Verified Apache is listening on port 6300.

